療保險得以保留，從球會領取的養老金將被下調，此外此前的免費球票或等價值的現金福利也被完全終止。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴呢d垃圾狗球隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0abfb26e35518a2b2286d9b42772588dc820964a","tid":2143234,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"此前在疫情期間，阿仙奴球會說服大部分球員降薪12.5%，就是表態要用球員降薪的這部分資金保住球會其他員工的工作，但如今球會卻一次性裁員10%，這令球員們非常失望。<br />\n<br />\n真心閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母 降薪條件係保就業<br />\n降完又炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d9d9267f9938c94081639a19998389a0b34fc7","tid":2143234,"uid":9247,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"0abfb26e35518a2b2286d9b42772588dc820964a","tid":2143234,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"此前在疫情期間，阿仙奴球會說服大部分球員降薪12.5%，就是表態要用球員降薪的這部分資金保住球會其他員工的工作，但如今球會卻一次性裁員10%，這令球員們非常失望。<br />\n<br />\n真心閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母 降薪條件係保就業<br />\n降完又炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"彈弓手真係好撚柒 個盃又係黑返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾阿"